.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, german, italian, thai, turkish
City: hamburg, miami, colone, prague, berlin, venice
1. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the thai##1
3. the person traveling to prague is between the italian and the argentine##2
4. the german is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
5. the argentine is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
7. the italian is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
8. the dutch is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Nationality   | dutch | turkish | thai | italian | german | argentine  |
| City           | venice | berlin  | hamburg | miami    | prague  | colone |

