.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
6 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, frog, guinea-pig, rabbit, snake
House: art-deco, wooden, victorian, craftsman, cottage, farmhouse
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the art-deco house##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the cottage house##1
3. the art-deco house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the art-deco house##2
7. the wooden house is on the far left##1
8. the victorian house is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Pet         | chinchilla | bird | snake      | rabbit | guinea-pig | frog      |
| House   | wooden    | farmhouse  | art-deco | craftsman   | cottage       | victorian |

