.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: drawing, photography, reading, hiking, woodworking, sudoku
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, roller, scooter, taxi, trike
1. the person driving the roller is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the bike and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Hobby        | photography    | sudoku | reading | drawing | woodworking | hiking   |
| Transport   | scooter | taxi        | quad-bike  | bike     | trike  | roller |

