2. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is the prince-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is between the siglo-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##2
7. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Hobby       | skydiving | hiking | chess | reading | gardening | cooking |
| Cigar   | game | prince    | alhambra  | blend    | siglo    | ritmeester    |

