.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
House: townhouse, cottage, victorian, gothic-revival, ranch-style, craftsman
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, disco, gospel, indie, jazz, trance
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of trance is between the fan of jazz and the fan of blues##2
4. the gothic-revival house is the fan of gospel##1
5. the victorian house is between the cottage house and the ranch-style house##2
6. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of trance##1
7. the ranch-style house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
8. the ranch-style house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
9. the victorian house is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| House           | gothic-revival | craftsman | ranch-style | victorian | cottage | townhouse |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | indie   | disco         | blues    | trance     | jazz     |

