 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching satire movies and the owner of the frog##2
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 7. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person watching animation movies##1
 9. the owner of the cat is between the person watching animation movies and the owner of the chinchilla##2
10. the owner of the hedgehog is the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | snake   | rabbit | frog       | hedgehog | cat    | chinchilla |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | disaster  | epic | animation      | martial-arts | romance        |

