 3. the nurse is the person driving the bike##1
 4. the software-developer is between the teacher and the person driving the scooter##2
 5. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the scooter and the videographer##2
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the bartender##1
 7. the nurse is on the far left##1
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the bartender##1
 9. the person driving the scooter is the bartender##1
