 7. the person who growsiris is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is camping##2
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
